# DEPLOY440: normalize line endings repo-wide. The repo was relocated off OneDrive
# (which had rewritten line endings), leaving the whole tree showing as modified and
# burying real diffs. text=auto+eol=lf makes git store LF and stop the CRLF/LF churn.
# After committing this file, run once: git add --renormalize . && git commit -m "normalize line endings"
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.xlsx binary
*.pptx binary
*.docx binary
